snippet.title: Bassmaster Fishing 2022 - Career Mode, Bassmaster Royale, Cross-Play Multiplayer!
snippet.description:
Bassmaster® Fishing 2022 is being released worldwide on all PlayStation and Xbox systems, Steam, and the Microsoft Store on October 28th. It will also be available on Day 1 with Xbox Game Pass.


Pre-Order Bassmaster Fishing 2022 now on PlayStation, Xbox and Steam!

🎮 Xbox - https://bit.ly/Bassmaster-Fishing-2022-Deluxe-Xbox
🎮 PS4/5 US - https://bit.ly/Bassmaster-Fishing-2022-Deluxe-PS-US 
🎮 PS4/5 EU - https://bit.ly/Bassmaster-Fishing-2022-Deluxe-PS-EU 
🖥️ Steam - https://bit.ly/Bassmaster-Fishing-2022-Steam 

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Find out more about Bassmaster Fishing 2022 here: 
http://bit.ly/BassmasterFishing22d 

Also, don't forget to sign up for the newsletter: 
http://bit.ly/Bassmaster22Register4
